definition: having or denoting a high range, the pitch range of the highest female voice, increase threefold
details:
adjective
- having or denoting a high range
= synonyms: soprano
- having more than one decidedly dissimilar aspects or qualities
= synonyms: double
- having three units or components or elements
= synonyms: triplex, ternary, triple
- three times as great or many
= example: three times as great or many
= synonyms: threefold
noun
- the pitch range of the highest female voice
= synonyms: soprano
verb
- increase threefold
= synonyms: triple
- sing treble
